	<Title>
		Detox diets: Do they work?
	</Title>
	<Abstract>
		Detox diets are popular, but they&apos;re not scientifically proven &amp;mdash; and may have harmful side effects.
	</Abstract>
	<Question>
		Do detox diets offer any health benefits?
